item.title: HackTheBox - Nibbles Writeup
item.description: Nmap Like always, I’m going to scan the IP address by using Nmap. However, today I feel spicier ;). So, I’m going to scan the full port with -p- then I’m only scanning those open ports with scripts and version enumeration. nmap -sCV -p22,80 -oN nmap/nibbles 10.10.10.75 22/tcp open ssh OpenSSH 7.2p2 Ubuntu 4ubuntu2.2 (Ubuntu Linux; protocol 2.0) | ssh-hostkey: | 2048 c4:f8:ad:e8:f8:04:77:de:cf:15:0d:63:0a:18:7e:49 (RSA) | 256 22:8f:b1:97:bf:0f:17:08:fc:7e:2c:8f:e9:77:3a:48 (ECDSA) |_ 256 e6:ac:27:a3:b5:a9:f1:12:3c:34:a5:5d:5b:eb:3d:e9 (ED25519) 80/tcp open http Apache httpd 2.
